title: World News | Ambassador Kwatra Outlines Three-sutra Framework for India AI Impact Summit, Stresses People-first Approach
description: Get latest articles and stories on World at LatestLY. Indian Ambassador Vinay Mohan Kwatra outlined India's people-first AI vision ahead of the India AI Impact Summit 2026, built on pillars of people, planet and progress. The Global South's first AI summit will focus on inclusive growth, responsible innovation and policy outcomes across India and developing nations.
